-- Enel Green Power Agrees on $340 Million EIB Loan for Portugal Wind
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2011-12-22T10:12:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-22/enel-green-power-agrees-on-340-million-eib-loan-for-portugal-wind.html
A consortium led by Enel Green Power
Espana SL agreed a 260 million-euro ($340 million) loan from the
 European Investment Bank  to fund 376 megawatts of wind parks in
 Portugal , the company said in a regulatory filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  